Improved Shield Bash		TYPE:General.Fighter.AttackOption																											PREMULT:1,[PREPROFWITHSHIELD:1,TYPE.Light],[PREFEAT:1,Shield Proficiency]																																	DESC:You can bash with a shield while retaining its shield bonus to your Armor Class.	BENEFIT:When you perform a shield bash, you may still apply the shield's shield bonus to your AC.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																			SOURCEPAGE:p.96	SOURCESHORT:PH
