Improved Trip			TYPE:General.Fighter.AttackOption													PREFEAT:1,Combat Expertise																														PRESTAT:1,INT=13																							DESC:You are trained not only in tripping opponents safely but also in following through with an attack.	BENEFIT:You do not provoke an attack of opportunity when you attempt to trip an opponent while you are unarmed and gain a +4 bonus on your Strength check to trip your opponent. If you trip an opponent in melee combat, you immediately get a melee attack against that opponent.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																					SOURCEPAGE:p.96	SOURCESHORT:PH
